{"lemma":"دِيمَة","slug":"دِيمَة","root":"د.#.م","root_slug":"د-_-م","root_link":"/words/roots/د-_-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13475","n13574"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13475","headword_ar":"دِيمَةٌ","root":"dwm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lasting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"continuous, and still rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, M, and TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarobN","text_ar":"ضَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain in which is neither thunder nor lightning; the least of which is the third of a day or the third of a night; and the most thereof, of any period:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dym","text_ar":"ديم"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain that continues some days:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain that continues long and is still, without thunder and lightning:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain that continues five days,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"six,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seven,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day and a night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dym","text_ar":"ديم"},{"kind":"text","text":", M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the least whereof is a third of a day or of a night; and the most thereof, of any period:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diyamN","text_ar":"دِيَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed [into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] in the pl. because it is changed in the sing., (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duyuwmN","text_ar":"دُيُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Abu-l-'Omeythil, T, K,) and [coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diyomN","text_ar":"دِيْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, T, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mudaAmN","text_ar":"مُدَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Hence other things are thus termed by way of comparison. (S.) It is said in a trad. (S, M) of 'Áïsheh, (M,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna Eamaluhu diymapF","text_ar":"كَانَ عَمَلُهُ دِيمَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His work was incessant"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but moderate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not excessive"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Msb;) referring to Mohammad; (T, S, M, Msb;) on her being asked if he preferred some days to others: (T:) she likened it to the rain termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dymp","text_ar":"ديمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in respect of continuance and moderation. (T, M.) And it is related of Hudheyfeh that he said, mentioning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fitan","text_ar":"فِتَن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. trials, or probations, or conflicts and factions, &c.],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahaA laA=tiyatukumo diymFA diymFA","text_ar":"اـِنَّهَا لَا=تِيَتُكُمْ دِيمًا دِيمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily they are coming to you"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filling the earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with continuance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","M","K","TA","S","T"]},{"entry_id":"n13574","headword_ar":"دِيمَةٌ","root":"dym","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dwm","text_ar":"دوم"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}